{"id":117,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":117,"title":"Acts 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul recounts the story of his conversion and also tells of seeing Jesus in a vision—He is accorded some privileges as a Roman citizen."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.1","order":"03.07.022.14285"},["b","1"],"Men, brethren, and fathers, hear ye my defence",["i","which I make"],"now unto you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.2","order":"03.07.022.14286"},["b","2"],"(And when they heard that he spake in the Hebrew tongue to them, they kept the more silence: and he saith,)"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3","order":"03.07.022.14287"},["b","3"],"I am verily a man",["i","which am"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Jew"],", born in Tarsus,",["i","a city"],"in Cilicia, yet brought up in this city at the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"feet"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"Gamaliel"],",",["i","and"],"taught according to the perfect manner of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"law"],"of the fathers, and was",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_3e"},"zealous"],"toward God, as ye all are this day."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.4","order":"03.07.022.14288"},["b","4"],"And I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"persecuted"],"this way unto the death, binding and delivering into prisons both men and women."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.5","order":"03.07.022.14289"},["b","5"],"As also the high priest doth bear me witness, and all the estate of the elders: from whom also I received",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"letters"],"unto the brethren, and went to Damascus, to bring them which were there bound unto Jerusalem, for to be punished."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.6","order":"03.07.022.14290"},["b","6"],"And it came to pass, that, as I made my journey, and was come nigh unto Damascus about noon, suddenly there shone from heaven a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"light"],"round about me."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.7","order":"03.07.022.14291"},["b","7"],"And I fell unto the ground, and heard a voice saying unto me,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Saul"],", Saul, why persecutest thou me?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.8","order":"03.07.022.14292"},["b","8"],"And I answered, Who art thou, Lord? And he said unto me, I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Jesus"],"of Nazareth, whom thou persecutest."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.9","order":"03.07.022.14293"},["b","9"],"And they that were with me saw indeed the light, and were afraid; but they heard not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"voice"],"of him that spake to me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.10","order":"03.07.022.14294"},["b","10"],"And I said, What shall I do, Lord? And the Lord said unto me, Arise, and go into Damascus; and there it shall be told thee of all things which are appointed for thee to do."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.11","order":"03.07.022.14295"},["b","11"],"And when I could not see for the glory of that light, being led by the hand of them that were with me, I came into Damascus."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.12","order":"03.07.022.14296"},["b","12"],"And one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Ananias"],", a devout man according to the law, having a good",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"report"],"of all the Jews which dwelt",["i","there,"]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.13","order":"03.07.022.14297"},["b","13"],"Came unto me, and stood, and said unto me, Brother Saul, receive thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sight"],". And the same hour I looked up upon him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.14","order":"03.07.022.14298"},["b","14"],"And he said, The God of our fathers hath chosen thee, that thou shouldest know his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"will"],", and see that Just One, and shouldest hear the voice of his mouth."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.15","order":"03.07.022.14299"},["b","15"],"For thou shalt be his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"witness"],"unto all men of what thou hast seen and heard."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.16","order":"03.07.022.14300"},["b","16"],"And now why tarriest thou? arise, and be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"baptized"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"wash"],"away thy sins, calling on the name of the Lord."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.17","order":"03.07.022.14301"},["b","17"],"And it came to pass, that, when I was come again to Jerusalem, even while I prayed in the temple, I was in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"trance"],";"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.18","order":"03.07.022.14302"},["b","18"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"saw"],"him saying unto me, Make haste, and get thee quickly out of Jerusalem: for they will not receive thy testimony concerning me."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.19","order":"03.07.022.14303"},["b","19"],"And I said, Lord, they know that I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"imprisoned"],"and beat in every synagogue them that believed on thee:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.20","order":"03.07.022.14304"},["b","20"],"And when the blood of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"martyr"],"Stephen was shed, I also was standing by, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"consenting"],"unto his death, and kept the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"raiment"],"of them that slew him."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.21","order":"03.07.022.14305"},["b","21"],"And he said unto me, Depart: for I will send thee far hence unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.22","order":"03.07.022.14306"},["b","22"],"And they gave him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"audience"],"unto this word, and",["i","then"],"lifted up their voices, and said, Away with such a",["i","fellow"],"from the earth: for it is not fit that he should live."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.23","order":"03.07.022.14307"},["b","23"],"And as they cried out, and cast off",["i","their"],"clothes, and threw dust into the air,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.24","order":"03.07.022.14308"},["b","24"],"The chief captain commanded him to be brought into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"castle"],", and bade that he should be examined by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"scourging"],"; that he might know wherefore they cried so against him."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.25","order":"03.07.022.14309"},["b","25"],"And as they bound him with thongs, Paul said unto the centurion that stood by, Is it lawful for you to scourge a man that is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Roman"],", and uncondemned?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.26","order":"03.07.022.14310"},["b","26"],"When the centurion heard",["i","that,"],"he went and told the chief captain, saying, Take heed what thou doest: for this man is a Roman."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.27","order":"03.07.022.14311"},["b","27"],"Then the chief captain came, and said unto him, Tell me, art thou a Roman? He said, Yea."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.28","order":"03.07.022.14312"},["b","28"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"chief"],"captain answered, With a great sum obtained I this freedom. And Paul said, But I was",["i","free"],"born."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.29","order":"03.07.022.14313"},["b","29"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Then"],"straightway they departed from him which should have examined him: and the chief captain also was afraid, after he knew that he was a Roman, and because he had bound him."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.30","order":"03.07.022.14314"},["b","30"],"On the morrow, because he would have known the certainty wherefore he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"accused"],"of the Jews, he loosed him from",["i","his"],"bands, and commanded the chief priests and all their council to appear, and brought Paul down, and set him before them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3a","order":"03.07.022.14315"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.1"},"Rom. 11:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3b","order":"03.07.022.14317"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.3"},"Deut. 33:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3c","order":"03.07.022.14319"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.34"},"Acts 5:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3d","order":"03.07.022.14321"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.5"},"Acts 26:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"3e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3e","order":"03.07.022.14323"},["b","3e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.4a","order":"03.07.022.14325"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.3"},"Acts 8:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.10"},"26:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.13"},"1 Tim. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.5a","order":"03.07.022.14327"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.2"},"Acts 9:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.6a","order":"03.07.022.14329"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.7a","order":"03.07.022.14331"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.4.1-9"},"Acts 9:4 (1–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.14.9-17"},"26:14 (9–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.8a","order":"03.07.022.14333"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.9"},"Acts 23:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.9a","order":"03.07.022.14335"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.7"},"Acts 9:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.12a","order":"03.07.022.14337"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.10"},"Acts 9:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.12b","order":"03.07.022.14339"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/3.7"},"1 Tim. 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.13a","order":"03.07.022.14341"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sight"},"TG Sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.14a","order":"03.07.022.14343"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-will-of"},"TG God, Will of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.15a","order":"03.07.022.14345"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.48.45-49"},"Luke 24:48 (45–49)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.15"},"Acts 9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/13.31.29-33"},"13:31 (29–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.16"},"26:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.16a","order":"03.07.022.14347"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-essential"},"Baptism, Essential"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.16b","order":"03.07.022.14349"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wash"},"TG Wash"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.17a","order":"03.07.022.14351"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.10.9-18"},"Acts 10:10 (9–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.5.1-18"},"11:5 (1–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.18a","order":"03.07.022.14353"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.19a","order":"03.07.022.14355"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.3.3-4"},"Acts 8:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.20a","order":"03.07.022.14357"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.20b","order":"03.07.022.14359"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.48.47-49"},"Luke 11:48 (47–49)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.20c","order":"03.07.022.14361"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.58"},"Acts 7:58"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.21a","order":"03.07.022.14363"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.17.17-18"},"Acts 26:17 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.13"},"Rom. 11:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.22a","order":"03.07.022.14365"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.32"},"2 Ne. 27:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.24a","order":"03.07.022.14367"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.34"},"Acts 21:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.24b","order":"03.07.022.14369"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.25a","order":"03.07.022.14371"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.37"},"Acts 16:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27"},"23:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.28a","order":"03.07.022.14373"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.26"},"Acts 23:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.29a","order":"03.07.022.14375"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-acts/22.29-30"},["span.small","JST"],"Acts 22:29–30 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.30a","order":"03.07.022.14377"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.28"},"Acts 23:28"],"."]]}
